dct_description_sm: Sheet 1: At the westernmost point is Port Street and Ave. R, continuing north to the Lehigh Valley and New York Bay RR. Continuing east is Newark Bay and south is the Port of Newark terminal.
Sheet 2: At the westernmost point is the shore line of Newark Bay, continuing north is the Port Newark Terminal, continuing east and south is the Newark Bay.
Maps also show the high water line north of Port Newark Terminal.
